# profile/CLAUDE.md — Your business context

> Private file. Gitignored. Layered on top of the framework `CLAUDE.md` at
> the repo root. AI assistants read both: the root file gives them the
> framework rules; this file gives them your business — who the user is,
> what the company sells, who the customers are, what the accounting
> policies are, which KPIs matter, how variance commentary should read.

Replace each `[bracketed placeholder]` below with your own content. The
[onboarding skill](../.claude/skills/onboarding/SKILL.md) does this
interactively if you'd rather not edit by hand.

---

